    完善<function>headline()</>函数中超长headline的处理(Teodor)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Prevent possible Assert failure or misconversion if an encoding
      conversion is created with the wrong conversion function for the
      specified pair of encodings (Tom, Heikki)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
     
 如果用错误的转换函数为指定编码对创建一个编码转换，
 防止可能的断言故障或错误转换。(Tom, Heikki)  
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix possible Assert failure if a statement executed in PL/pgSQL is
      rewritten into another kind of statement, for example if an
      <command>INSERT</> is rewritten into an <command>UPDATE</> (Heikki)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
      修复可能的断言失败，如果在PL/pgSQL中执行语句改写成另一种语句，
  例如，如果<command>INSERT</>改写为<command>UPDATE</> (Heikki)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Ensure that a snapshot is available to datatype input functions (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
     确保快照可用于数据类型输入函数(Tom)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      This primarily affects domains that are declared with <literal>CHECK</>
      constraints involving user-defined stable or immutable functions.  Such
      functions typically fail if no snapshot has been set.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
      这主要影响了声明为涉及用户定义的稳定或者不变函数<literal>CHECK</>
限制的域。如果没有设置快照，则这样的函数往往失败。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Make it safer for SPI-using functions to be used within datatype I/O;
      in particular, to be used in domain check constraints (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
     为用于数据类型I/O中SPI使用函数使其更安全；
 特别是用于域检查约束(Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Avoid unnecessary locking of small tables in <command>VACUUM</>
      (Heikki)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    避免<command>VACUUM</>中小表的不必要锁定(Heikki) 
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix a problem that sometimes kept <command>ALTER TABLE ENABLE/DISABLE
      RULE</> from being recognized by active sessions (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
   修复保持<command>ALTER TABLE ENABLE/DISABLE RULE</>被活跃会话识别的问题(Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix a problem that made <literal>UPDATE RETURNING tableoid</>
      return zero instead of the correct OID (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
   修复使用<literal>UPDATE RETURNING tableoid</>返回零而不是正确OID问题(Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Allow functions declared as taking <type>ANYARRAY</> to work on
      the <structname>pg_statistic</> columns of that type (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    允许函数声明为采用<type>ANYARRAY</>以便在该类型的<structname>pg_statistic</>列上执行(Tom)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      This used to work, but was unintentionally broken in 8.3.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    这曾经运行，但是在8.3中无意被损坏。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix planner misestimation of selectivity when transitive equality
      is applied to an outer-join clause (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
     当转变的平等应用于外部连接子句的时候，修复选择性的规划器误评估(Tom)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      This could result in bad plans for queries like
      <literal>... from a left join b on a.a1 = b.b1 where a.a1 = 42 ...</>
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    这可能会导致查询不好的规划像<literal>... from a left join b on a.a1 = b.b1 where a.a1 = 42 ...</>。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Improve optimizer's handling of long <literal>IN</> lists (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
   完善长<literal>IN</>列表的优化处理(Tom)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      This change avoids wasting large amounts of time on such lists
      when constraint exclusion is enabled.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    当启用约束排除的时候，该变化避免了在列表上浪费大量时间。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Prevent synchronous scan during GIN index build (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    防止在GIN索引构建期间同步扫描(Tom)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Because GIN is optimized for inserting tuples in increasing TID order,
      choosing to use a synchronous scan could slow the build by a factor of
      three or more.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
     由于GIN是在增加TID顺序中为插入元组进行了优化，
选择使用同步扫描可能会减缓通过三个或更多个因素的编译。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Ensure that the contents of a holdable cursor don't depend on the
      contents of TOAST tables (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
     确保持有游标的内容不依赖于TOAST表的内容(Tom)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Previously, large field values in a cursor result might be represented
      as TOAST pointers, which would fail if the referenced table got dropped
      before the cursor is read, or if the large value is deleted and then
      vacuumed away.  This cannot happen with an ordinary cursor,
      but it could with a cursor that is held past its creating transaction.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
      此前，游标中大字段值可能会表示为TOAST指针，如果引用的表在读取游标之前被删除，
或者如果大值被删除，然后清理。这可能失败。这不能发生在普通游标中，
但它可能使用游标保持超过它创建的事务。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix memory leak when a set-returning function is terminated without
      reading its whole result (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    当一组返回函数没有读取整个结果而被终止，那么修复内存泄露(Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix encoding conversion problems in XML functions when the database
      encoding isn't UTF-8 (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    当数据库编码不是UTF-8的时候，修复XML函数中编码转换问题(Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix <filename>contrib/dblink</>'s
      <function>dblink_get_result(text,bool)</> function (Joe)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
   修复<filename>contrib/dblink</>的<function>dblink_get_result(text,bool)</>函数(Joe)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix possible garbage output from <filename>contrib/sslinfo</> functions
      (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    修复来自<filename>contrib/sslinfo</>函数的垃圾输出(Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix incorrect behavior of <filename>contrib/tsearch2</> compatibility
      trigger when it's fired more than once in a command (Teodor)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    当在命令中被触发一次以上的时候，修复<filename>contrib/tsearch2</>兼容性触发器的
不正确操作(Teodor)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix possible mis-signaling in autovacuum (Heikki)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
   修复autovacuum中可能错误信号(Heikki)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Support running as a service on Windows 7 beta (Dave and Magnus)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
     支持作为Windows 7 beta服务运行(Dave和Magnus)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix <application>ecpg</>'s handling of varchar structs (Michael)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    修复varchar结构<application>ecpg</>的处理(Michael)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix <application>configure</> script to properly report failure when
      unable to obtain linkage information for PL/Perl (Andrew)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    当无法获得PL/Perl连接信息的时候，修复<application>configure</>脚本用来正确报告
错误(Andrew)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Make all documentation reference <literal>pgsql-bugs</> and/or
      <literal>pgsql-hackers</> as appropriate, instead of the
      now-decommissioned <literal>pgsql-ports</> and <literal>pgsql-patches</>
      mailing lists (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
   使用适当的所有文档引用<literal>pgsql-bugs</> 和/或者<literal>pgsql-hackers</>，
   而不是现在过时的<literal>pgsql-ports</>和<literal>pgsql-patches</>邮件列表(Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Update time zone data files to <application>tzdata</> release 2009a (for
      Kathmandu and historical DST corrections in Switzerland, Cuba)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    （为Kathmandu和Switzerland, Cuba中历史DST）更新时区数据文件到<application>tzdata</>发布2009a 
</para>
    </listitem>

   </itemizedlist>

  </sect2>
 </sect1>

 <sect1 id="release-8-3-5">
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
  <title>Release 8.3.5</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
  <title>版本8.3.5</title>

  <formalpara>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
  <title>Release date:</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
  <title>发布日期：</title>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
  <para>2008-11-03</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
  <para>2008-11-03</para>
  </formalpara>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
   This release contains a variety of fixes from 8.3.4.
   For information about new features in the 8.3 major release, see
   <xref linkend="release-8-3">.
  </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    该发布包含来自8.3.4各种修复。关于8.3主要发布中新特性信息，
参阅<xref linkend="release-8-3">。
</para>

  <sect2>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
   <title>Migration to Version 8.3.5</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
   <title>迁移到版本8.3.5</title>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
    A dump/restore is not required for those running 8.3.X.
    However, if you are upgrading from a version earlier than 8.3.1,
    see <xref linkend="release-8-3-1">.  Also, if you were running a previous
    8.3.X release, it is recommended to <command>REINDEX</> all GiST
    indexes after the upgrade.
   </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
   运行8.3.X不需要备份/恢复。然而，如果从8.3.1更早版本更新，参阅8.3.1发布说明。
   另外，如果你正在运行之前的8.3.X版本，推荐更新之后<command>REINDEX</>所有
   GiST索引。
</para>

  </sect2>

  <sect2>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
   <title>Changes</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
   <title>变化</title>
   <itemizedlist>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix GiST index corruption due to marking the wrong index entry
      <quote>dead</> after a deletion (Teodor)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
     修复GiST索引损坏，由于在删除之后标记错误索引项<quote>死的</>(Teodor)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      This would result in index searches failing to find rows they
      should have found.  Corrupted indexes can be fixed with
      <command>REINDEX</>.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    这可能导致索引搜索无法找到他们应该找的行。
损坏的索引可以使用<command>REINDEX</>被修复。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix backend crash when the client encoding cannot represent a localized
      error message (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    当客户端编码不能表示本地化错误消息的时候，修复后台崩溃(Tom)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      We have addressed similar issues before, but it would still fail if
      the <quote>character has no equivalent</> message itself couldn't
      be converted.  The fix is to disable localization and send the plain
      ASCII error message when we detect such a situation.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
   我们已经解决了之前类似问题，如果<quote>字符没有等同</>消息自身不能被转化，
   但是可能仍然失败。当我们发现这种情况的时候，解决办法是禁用本地化并且发送
   纯ASCII错误消息。   
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix possible crash in <type>bytea</>-to-XML mapping (Michael McMaster)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
   修复<type>bytea</>到XML映射中可能崩溃(Michael McMaster) 
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix possible crash when deeply nested functions are invoked from
      a trigger (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    当深度嵌套函数被触发器调用的时候，修复可能崩溃(Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Improve optimization of <replaceable>expression</> <literal>IN</>
      (<replaceable>expression-list</>) queries (Tom, per an idea from Robert
      Haas)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    提高<replaceable>expression</> <literal>IN</>(<replaceable>expression-list</>)查询优化(Tom,每一个想法都来自Robert Haas) 
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Cases in which there are query variables on the right-hand side had been
      handled less efficiently in 8.2.x and 8.3.x than in prior versions.
      The fix restores 8.1 behavior for such cases.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    右边有查询变量比起之前版本已经在8.2.x和8.3.x中被低效处理，
该修复为这种情况修复了8.1操作。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix mis-expansion of rule queries when a sub-<literal>SELECT</> appears
      in a function call in <literal>FROM</>,  a multi-row <literal>VALUES</>
      list, or a <literal>RETURNING</> list (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    当子<literal>SELECT</>出现在<literal>FROM</>，
多行<literal>VALUES</>列表，或者<literal>RETURNING</>列表中的函数调用中的时候，修复规则查询的错误扩展(Tom)  
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      The usual symptom of this problem is an <quote>unrecognized node type</>
      error.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    这个问题的常见现象是<quote>未知节点类型</>错误。 
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix Assert failure during rescan of an <literal>IS NULL</>
      search of a GiST index (Teodor)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
     在GiST索引的<literal>IS NULL</>搜索的重复扫描中，修复断言失败(Teodor)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix memory leak during rescan of a hashed aggregation plan (Neil)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    在散列聚合规划的重复扫描中，修复内存泄露(Neil) 
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Ensure an error is reported when a newly-defined PL/pgSQL trigger
      function is invoked as a normal function (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    当新定义PL/pgSQL触发器函数作为正常函数被调用的时候，
确保报告一个错误(Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Force a checkpoint before <command>CREATE DATABASE</> starts to copy
      files (Heikki)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
   在<command>CREATE DATABASE</>开始拷贝文件之前，强迫检查点(Heikki)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      This prevents a possible failure if files had recently been deleted
      in the source database.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
   如果在源数据库中已经删除了文件，这可以防止可能错误。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Prevent possible collision of <structfield>relfilenode</> numbers
      when moving a table to another tablespace with <command>ALTER SET
      TABLESPACE</> (Heikki)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    当移动表到另外一个使用<command>ALTER SET TABLESPACE</>的表空间时，预防<structfield>relfilenode</>数的可能冲突(Heikki) 
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      The command tried to re-use the existing filename, instead of
      picking one that is known unused in the destination directory.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    该命令尝试重新使用已有文件名，而不是选择在目标目录中未使用的一个。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix incorrect text search headline generation when single query
      item matches first word of text (Sushant Sinha)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    当单个查询项匹配文本第一个字的时候，修复不正确文本搜索headline生成(Sushant Sinha) 
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix improper display of fractional seconds in interval values when
      using a non-ISO datestyle in an <option>-&minus;enable-integer-datetimes</>
      build (Ron Mayer)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    当在<option>--enable-integer-datetimes</>编译中使用非ISO日期类型时，
修复间隔值中小数秒不正确显示(Ron Mayer)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Make <literal>ILIKE</> compare characters case-insensitively
      even when they're escaped (Andrew)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
   当他们被转义的时候，使用<literal>ILIKE</>比较字符不区分大小写(Andrew)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Ensure <command>DISCARD</> is handled properly by statement logging (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
   确保<command>DISCARD</>通过语句记录被正确处理(Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix incorrect logging of last-completed-transaction time during
      PITR recovery (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    在PITR恢复期间修复最后完成事务时不正确记录(Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Ensure <function>SPI_getvalue</> and <function>SPI_getbinval</>
      behave correctly when the passed tuple and tuple descriptor have
      different numbers of columns (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    当传递的元组以及元组描述符有不同列数时，确保<function>SPI_getvalue</>和<function>SPI_getbinval</>
正确操作(Tom)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      This situation is normal when a table has had columns added or removed,
      but these two functions didn't handle it properly.
      The only likely consequence is an incorrect error indication.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    当表中有列被添加或者删除的时候，这种情况是正常的，
但是这两个函数不能正确处理它。唯一可能后果是不正确错误显示。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Mark <varname>SessionReplicationRole</> as <literal>PGDLLIMPORT</>
      so it can be used by <application>Slony</> on Windows (Magnus)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    标记<varname>SessionReplicationRole</>为<literal>PGDLLIMPORT</>，
因此它可以用于Windows上<application>Slony</> (Magnus)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix small memory leak when using <application>libpq</>'s
      <literal>gsslib</> parameter (Magnus)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    当使用<application>libpq</>的<literal>gsslib</>参数的时候，
修复小的内存泄露(Magnus)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      The space used by the parameter string was not freed at connection
      close.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    在连接关闭时不释放通过参数字符串使用的空格。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Ensure <application>libgssapi</> is linked into <application>libpq</>
      if needed (Markus Schaaf)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    如果需要，那么确保<application>libgssapi</>被连接到<application>libpq</>中(Markus Schaaf)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix <application>ecpg</>'s parsing of <command>CREATE ROLE</> (Michael)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    修复<command>CREATE ROLE</>的<application>ecpg</>的解析(Michael) 
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix recent breakage of <literal>pg_ctl restart</> (Tom)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    修复<literal>pg_ctl restart</>最近破损(Tom)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Ensure <filename>pg_control</> is opened in binary mode
      (Itagaki Takahiro)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    确保以二进制模式打开<filename>pg_control</>(Itagaki Takahiro)
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      <application>pg_controldata</> and <application>pg_resetxlog</>
      did this incorrectly, and so could fail on Windows.
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
   <application>pg_controldata</>和<application>pg_resetxlog</>这样做不正确，
   因此在Windows上可能失败。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Update time zone data files to <application>tzdata</> release 2008i (for
      DST law changes in Argentina, Brazil, Mauritius, Syria)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    更新时区数据文件到<application>tzdata</>发布2008i (为Argentina, Brazil, Mauritius, Syria中DST变化）
    
</para>
    </listitem>

   </itemizedlist>

  </sect2>
 </sect1>

 <sect1 id="release-8-3-4">
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
   <title>Release 8.3.4</title>
