     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
  8.1中不允许，但是在8.2和8.3中无意中损坏了该检查。
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Fix rare crash when an error occurs during a query using a hash index
