 <sect1 id="release-8-3">
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
  <title>Release 8.3</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
  <title>版本8.3</title>
  <formalpara>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
   <title>Release date:</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
   <title>发布日期：</title>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
   <para>2008-02-04</para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
   <para>2008-02-04</para>
  </formalpara>

  <sect2>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
   <title>Overview</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
   <title>概述</title>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
    With significant new functionality and performance enhancements,
    this release represents a major leap forward for
    <productname>PostgreSQL</>. This was made possible by a growing
    community that has dramatically accelerated the pace of
    development. This release adds the following major features:
   </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    随着显著的新功能和性能增强，此版本对于<productname>PostgreSQL</>是一个重大的飞跃。
通过越来越多的社区已经大大加快了发展的步伐成为可能。此版本增加了以下主要特性：
</para>

   <itemizedlist>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Full text search is integrated into the core database system
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
   全文搜索被集合到核心数据库系统中
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Support for the SQL/XML standard, including new operators and an
      <type>XML</type> data type
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    支持SQL/XML标准，包含新的操作以及<type>XML</type>数据类型
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Enumerated data types (<type>ENUM</type>)
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    枚举数据类型(<type>ENUM</type>) 
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Arrays of composite types
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    复合类型数组
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Universally Unique Identifier (<type>UUID</>) data type
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
   通用唯一标识符(<type>UUID</>)数据类型 
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Add control over whether <literal>NULL</>s sort first or last
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    添加控制是否<literal>NULL</>首先排序还是最后排序
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Updatable cursors
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
   可更新游标
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Server configuration parameters can now be set on a per-function
      basis
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
   服务器配置参数可以基于每个函数被设置 
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      User-defined types can now have type modifiers
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
   用户定义类型可以有类型修饰符
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Automatically re-plan cached queries when table
      definitions change or statistics are updated
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    当更新表定义变化或者统计的时候，自动重新规划缓存查询
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Numerous improvements in logging and statistics collection
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    记录和统计收集中大量优化
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Support Security Service Provider Interface (<acronym>SSPI</>) for
      authentication on Windows
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    为Windows上认证支持安全服务提供者接口(<acronym>SSPI</>)
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Support multiple concurrent autovacuum processes, and other
      autovacuum improvements
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    支持多个并发autovacuum进程，和其它autovacuum优化
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Allow the whole <productname>PostgreSQL</> distribution to be compiled
      with <productname>Microsoft Visual C++</>
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
   允许使用<productname>Microsoft Visual C++</>编译整个<productname>PostgreSQL</>发布
</para>
    </listitem>

   </itemizedlist>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
    Major performance improvements are listed below.  Most of
    these enhancements are automatic and do not require user changes or
    tuning:
   </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    主要性能改进如下。大部分这些功能是自动的，不需要用户改变或者调整：
</para>

  <itemizedlist>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Asynchronous commit delays writes to WAL during transaction commit
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
   在事务提交期间异步提交延迟写入WAL
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Checkpoint writes can be spread over a longer time period to smooth
      the I/O spike during each checkpoint
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    检查点写操作被分散在一个较长时间周期内用来平滑每个检查点中I/O剧增
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Heap-Only Tuples (<acronym>HOT</>) accelerate space reuse for
      most <command>UPDATE</>s and <command>DELETE</>s
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
     堆元组(<acronym>HOT</>)加快了大部分<command>UPDATE</>和<command>DELETE</>的 
 空间复用 
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Just-in-time background writer strategy improves disk write
      efficiency
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    及时后端写策略提高了磁盘写效率 
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Using non-persistent transaction IDs for read-only transactions
      reduces overhead and <command>VACUUM</> requirements
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    为只读事务使用非持久事务ID减少开销和<command>VACUUM</>需求
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Per-field and per-row storage overhead has been reduced
     </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
   减少每个字段和每行存储开销
</para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
      Large sequential scans no longer force out frequently used
      cached pages
     </para>
