<title>Build Options</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<title>编译选项</title>

    <itemizedlist>

     <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
       Add <application>configure</> option <literal>-&minus;enable-profiling</>
       to enable code profiling (works only with <application>gcc</>)
       (Korry Douglas and Nikhil Sontakke)
      </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    添加<application>configure</>选项<literal>--enable-profiling</>
    用来启动代码分析(使用<application>gcc</>执行)(Korry Douglas和Nikhil Sontakke)
</para>
     </listitem>

     <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
       Add <application>configure</> option <literal>-&minus;with-system-tzdata</>
       to use the operating system's time zone database (Peter)
      </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
   添加<application>configure</>选项<literal>--with-system-tzdata</>用来
   使用操作系统的时区数据库(Peter)
</para>
     </listitem>

     <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
       Fix <acronym>PGXS</> so extensions can be built against PostgreSQL
       installations whose <application>pg_config</> program does not
       appear first in the <varname>PATH</> (Tom)
      </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    修复<acronym>PGXS</>，以致于扩展会不利于PostgreSQL的安装，其中
<application>pg_config</>程序没有首先出现在<varname>PATH</>中(Tom)
</para>
     </listitem>

     <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
       Support <command>gmake draft</command> when building the
       <acronym>SGML</> documentation (Bruce)
      </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    当构建<acronym>SGML</>文档的时候，支持<command>gmake draft</command> (Bruce) 
</para>

<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
       Unless <literal>draft</> is used, the documentation build will
       now be repeated if necessary to ensure the index is up-to-date.
      </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    除非使用<literal>draft</>，如果确保索引是最新的，那么文档建立将被重复。 
</para>
     </listitem>

    </itemizedlist>

   </sect3>

   <sect3>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<title>Source Code</title>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<title>源代码</title> 

    <itemizedlist>

     <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
       Rename macro <literal>DLLIMPORT</> to <literal>PGDLLIMPORT</> to
       avoid conflicting with third party includes (like Tcl) that
       define <literal>DLLIMPORT</> (Magnus)
      </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    重命名宏<literal>DLLIMPORT</>到
<literal>PGDLLIMPORT</>以避免与包含（像Tcl）定义<literal>DLLIMPORT</>的第三方冲突 (Magnus)
</para>
     </listitem>

     <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
       Create <quote>operator families</quote> to improve planning of
       queries involving cross-data-type comparisons (Tom)
      </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    创建<quote>操作符类</quote>用来改善涉及交叉数据类型比较的查询规划(Tom)
</para>
     </listitem>

     <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
       Update GIN <function>extractQuery()</> API to allow signalling
       that nothing can satisfy the query (Teodor)
      </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    更新GIN <function>extractQuery()</> API允许发送信号没什么可以满足查询(Teodor)
</para>
     </listitem>

     <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
       Move <literal>NAMEDATALEN</> definition from
       <filename>postgres_ext.h</> to <filename>pg_config_manual.h</>
       (Peter)
      </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
   删除从<filename>postgres_ext.h</>到<filename>pg_config_manual.h</>的<literal>NAMEDATALEN</>定义(Peter)
</para>
     </listitem>

     <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
       Provide <function>strlcpy()</function> and
       <function>strlcat()</function> on all platforms, and replace
       error-prone uses of <function>strncpy()</function>,
       <function>strncat()</function>, etc (Peter)
      </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
   在所有平台上提供<function>strlcpy()</function>和<function>strlcat()</function>，
   并且替换<function>strncpy()</function>，<function>strncat()</function>的易出错的用法，等(Peter)
</para>
     </listitem>

     <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
       Create hooks to let an external plugin monitor (or even replace) the
       planner and create plans for hypothetical situations (Gurjeet
       Singh, Tom)
      </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
   创建钩子以便使外部插件监听（或者甚至替换）规划器并且为假设情况创建规划(Gurjeet Singh, Tom)
</para>
     </listitem>

     <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
       Create a function variable <literal>join_search_hook</> to let plugins
       override the join search order portion of the planner (Julius
       Stroffek)
      </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    创建函数变量<literal>join_search_hook</>让插件覆盖规划器的连接搜索顺序部分(Julius Stroffek)
</para>
     </listitem>

     <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
       Add <function>tas()</> support for Renesas' M32R processor
       (Kazuhiro Inaoka)
      </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    添加<function>tas()</>支持Renesas的M32R处理器(Kazuhiro Inaoka)
</para>
     </listitem>

     <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
       <function>quote_identifier()</function> and
       <application>pg_dump</application> no longer quote keywords that are
       unreserved according to the grammar (Tom)
      </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
     <function>quote_identifier()</function>和<application>pg_dump</application>
 不再引用依据语法未保留的关键字(Tom)
</para>
     </listitem>

     <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
       Change the on-disk representation of the <type>NUMERIC</type>
       data type so that the <structfield>sign_dscale</> word comes
       before the weight (Tom)
      </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
     改变<type>NUMERIC</type>数据类型的磁盘上的表示，以致于<structfield>sign_dscale</>词在权重之前(Tom)
</para>
     </listitem>

     <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
       Use <acronym>SYSV</> semaphores rather than POSIX on Darwin
       &gt;= 6.0, i.e., macOS 10.2 and up (Chris Marcellino)
      </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
     使用<acronym>SYSV</>信号而不是<acronym>SYSV</> &gt;= 6.0,即macOS 10.2及以上的POSIX(Chris Marcellino)
</para>
     </listitem>

     <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
       Add <link linkend="acronyms">acronym</link> and <link
       linkend="creating-cluster-nfs">NFS</link> documentation
       sections (Bruce)
      </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
    添加<link linkend="acronyms">acronym</link>和
<link linkend="creating-cluster-nfs">NFS</link>文档部分(Bruce)
</para>
     </listitem>

     <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
       "Postgres" is now documented as an accepted alias for
       "PostgreSQL" (Peter)
      </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
     "Postgres"作为"PostgreSQL"的公认别名(Peter) 
</para>
     </listitem>

     <listitem>
<!--==========================orignal english content==========================
<para>
       Add documentation about preventing database server spoofing when
       the server is down (Bruce)
      </para>
____________________________________________________________________________-->
<para>
     当服务器关闭的时候，添加关于避免数据库服务器欺骗的文档(Bruce)
</para>
     </listitem>

    </itemizedlist>

   </sect3>

